title: Add new game called Dice where you can bet under 5 or over 5 and get rewards. 50% of daily $Cake winning to be burned.
body: We create a new game called Dice like the ones from Tron or Ethereum, a player can bet $Cake for a random generated number and can win more cake, 50% of the lost $cake will be burned every 24h and 50% of the winnings go back into the winnings so we have a treasury to pay the winners.
choices: Yes, add dice game near Lottery so more $Cake is burned
author: 0x3F52fb161DF67C3204b3AdE93a9a6b0ef6DC6b46
